    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Xử lý Exception trong Java</title>
      <link>https://vuminhthien5.github.io/posts/xu-ly-exception-java/</link>
      <pubDate>Sat, 04 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vuminhthien5.github.io/posts/xu-ly-exception-java/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-exception-là-gì&#34;&gt;1. Exception là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Exception là các lỗi xảy ra trong quá trình thực thi chương trình.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-cách-xử-lý-exception&#34;&gt;2. Cách xử lý Exception&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Java sử dụng khối &lt;code&gt;try - catch&lt;/code&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;try&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; a &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt; 10 &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;/&lt;/span&gt; 0;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;} &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;catch&lt;/span&gt; (Exception e) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    System.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Có lỗi xảy ra&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010&#34;&gt;##&lt;/span&gt; 3. Ý nghĩa
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Giúp chương trình không bị dừng đột ngột khi gặp lỗi.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010&#34;&gt;##&lt;/span&gt; 4. Kết luận
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Xử lý Exception giúp chương trình ổn định hơn.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Lập trình hướng đối tượng trong Java</title>
      <link>https://vuminhthien5.github.io/posts/lap-trinh-huong-doi-tuong-java/</link>
      <pubDate>Fri, 03 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vuminhthien5.github.io/posts/lap-trinh-huong-doi-tuong-java/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-oop-là-gì&#34;&gt;1. OOP là gì?&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Lập trình hướng đối tượng (OOP) là phương pháp lập trình dựa trên các đối tượng.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-4-tính-chất-của-oop&#34;&gt;2. 4 tính chất của OOP&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Đóng gói&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Kế thừa&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Đa hình&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Trừu tượng&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;3-ví-dụ-class-trong-java&#34;&gt;3. Ví dụ Class trong Java&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;SinhVien&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    String ten;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;int&lt;/span&gt; tuoi;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;hienThi&lt;/span&gt;() {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        System.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(ten &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34; - &amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;+&lt;/span&gt; tuoi);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010&#34;&gt;##&lt;/span&gt; 4. Kết luận
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;OOP giúp chương trình dễ bảo trì và mở rộng.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Cấu trúc chương trình Java cơ bản</title>
      <link>https://vuminhthien5.github.io/posts/cau-truc-chuong-trinh-java/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>https://vuminhthien5.github.io/posts/cau-truc-chuong-trinh-java/</guid>
      <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;1-cấu-trúc-tổng-quát&#34;&gt;1. Cấu trúc tổng quát&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Một chương trình Java cơ bản gồm:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Package&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Import&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Class&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Hàm main&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;h2 id=&#34;2-ví-dụ-chương-trình-java-đơn-giản&#34;&gt;2. Ví dụ chương trình Java đơn giản&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; style=&#34;color:#f8f8f2;background-color:#272822;-moz-tab-size:4;-o-tab-size:4;tab-size:4;&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-java&#34; data-lang=&#34;java&#34;&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;class&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;HelloWorld&lt;/span&gt; {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;public&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;static&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#66d9ef&#34;&gt;void&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;main&lt;/span&gt;(String&lt;span style=&#34;color:#f92672&#34;&gt;[]&lt;/span&gt; args) {
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;        System.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;out&lt;/span&gt;.&lt;span style=&#34;color:#a6e22e&#34;&gt;println&lt;/span&gt;(&lt;span style=&#34;color:#e6db74&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Hello Java&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;);
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;    }
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;}
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;color:#960050;background-color:#1e0010&#34;&gt;##&lt;/span&gt; 3. Kết Luận
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&#34;display:flex;&#34;&gt;&lt;span&gt;Nắm vững cấu trúc chương trình là bước đầu quan trọng khi học Java.
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
    </item>
